The paper deals with machine perception of audio events and the generation of natural language descriptions for audio scenes. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing). The paper also involves natural language processing and generation, which falls under cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper uses machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper involves the creation of a dataset, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
